examples.en: He was bubbling with good humour.
Look out! The pan of milk is bubbling over!
The water was bubbling away on the stove.
Resentment was still bubbling inside her.
I use pie weights to keep the pie crust from bubbling when I bake it.
We were ravenous after our canoe paddling, and the chili bubbling over the campfire smelled heavenly.
